    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The collective bodies of religious and lay counselors, officers, courtiers, family members, and attendants constituting the retinue of a pope. For the judicial bodies of popes, use "papal tribunals."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
